-- Ace Has Commodity Hedges to Guard Crop Insurance, Greenberg Says
-- B y   M a r c i   J a c o b s
-- 2013-10-23T13:04:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-23/ace-has-commodity-hedges-to-guard-crop-insurance-greenberg-says.html
Ace Ltd. (ACE) , the insurer with
operations in more than 50 nations, has hedges to guard against
declines in commodity prices that could pressure results at
units protecting farmers against crop losses.  “We do a little hedging, but modestly,” Chief Executive
Officer Evan Greenberg said on a conference call today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
